text: Tijeras is a corregimiento in Boquerón District, Chiriquí Province, Panama. It has a land area of and had a population of 2,670 as of 2010, giving it a population density of . Its population as of 1990 was 1,341; its population as of 2000 was 2,057. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Chiriquí Province
